quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif Laaam Raa ا. yeh khuda ki kitaab aur quran roshan ki ayatain hain
  15,2,kisi waqt kafir log arzoo karen ge ke ae kash woh musalman hotay
  15,3,( ae Mohammad ) un ko unn ke haal par rehne do ke khalin aur faiday athaliN aur ( tole ) Amal un ko duniya mein mashgool kiye rahay anqareeb un ko ( is ka injaam ) maloom ho jaye ga
  15,4,aur hum ne koi bastii halaak nahi ki. magar is ka waqt marqoom o moayan tha
  15,5,koi jamaat apni muddat ( wafaat ) se nah agay nikal sakti hai nah peechay reh sakti hai
  15,6,aur kufar kehte hain ke ae shakhs jis par nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) nazil hui hai too to deewana hai
  15,7,agar to sacha hai to hamaray paas firshton ko kyun nahi le aata
  15,8,( keh do ) hum firshton ko nazil nahikiya karte magar haq ke sath aur is waqt un ko mohlat nahi millti
  15,9,be shak yeh ( kitaab ) nasiyaat hamein ne aُtari hai aur hum hi is ke nigehbaan hain
  15,10,aur hum ne tum se pehlay logon mein bhi paighambar beje they
  15,11,aur unn ke paas koi paighambar nahi aata tha magar woh uss ke sathistehzaa karte they
  15,12,isi terhan hum is ( takzib o zalal ) ko gunahgaaron ke dilon mein daakhil kar dete hain
  15,13,so woh is par imaan nahi laatay aur pehloo ki rawish bhi yahi rahi hai
  15,14,avragr hum aasman ka koi darwaaza unn par khol den aur woh is mein charhne bhi lagen
  15,15,to bhi yahi kahin ke hamari ankhen makhmoor hogayi hain balkay hum par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai
